        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 6. Caspia baerii Clessin & Dybowski in Dybowski, 1887 from the Caspian Sea. (a–c) Lectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 96). (d) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 96). (e, k, o, r) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 96). (f, l, p, s). Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 97). (g, h) Specimen labelled as “Caspia tadjallipouri, holotype”, locality 7 (ZIN, no number). (i, j) Specimen labelled as “Caspia tadjallipouri, paratype”, locality 7 (ZIN, no number). (m, n) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 95). (q) Specimen labelled as “Caspia tadjallipouri, paratype”, locality 7 (ZIN, no number). Scale bars = 1 mm (a–n), 100 μm (o–s)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4550164/files/figure.png" .

